result.name: Bear's lab

reviews.text: I always come here because drink & service are great. But today I told the staff the drink wasn’t good and she turn to very rude and bad temper. I will never come here again, very disappointed.
I had the Acai bowl which was very tasty, along with the hot turmeric coffee (which was a unique taste but complemented the bowl well). Small place but I went on a Sunday afternoon so was quiet.
The food is nice and fresh. A bit too expensive.
Favourite place to get fruit bowls in HK. Very tasty, friendly staff. Love it!
Little bit pricy but it's so tastyyyyy!! For your green Day, it's the best choice for the full and guiltless lunch, and u know what, all the bowl is only have 200-300 cal! IMPOSSIBLE!!!!
